<P>__{(synthesized voice)}
<D>__{she didn't call.}
<A>__{mike collapses into his futon and lights a smoke. beat. he pulls out the cocktail napkin. he stares at the number. he looks at the clock. 2:20 am. he looks at the napkin. he thinks better of it, and puts the napkin away. beat. he takes out the napkin and picks up the phone.}
